    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who make tools for delicate or precision work.  For those who make musical instruments, use "musical instrument makers." For those who specifically make,  design, or repair stringed instruments of the lute, harp, viol, and violin families, such as guitars, frame harps, violas da gamba, and violins, see "luthiers."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000031151/Supplement to the OED (1972-1986)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aquellos que fabrican herramientas para trabajo delicado o de precisión. Para aquellos que hacen instrumentos musicales, construyen "la frase", "instrumento musical" + "fabricante". Para aquellos que hacen, diseñan o reparan instrumentos de cuerda laúd, arpa, viola, y familia de los violines, como la guitarra, arpas de bastidor, viola da gamba, y para violines, vea "luthiers."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Zij die gereedschappen maken voor fijn werk of precisiewerk. Combineer 'muziekinstrument' + 'makers' voor personen die muziekinstrumenten maken. Zie 'makers van snaarinstrumenten' voor hen die specifiek snaarinstrumenten maken, ontwerpen of repareren uit de families van de luit, harp, viola en viool, zoals gitaren, lijstharpen, viola da gamba’s en violen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
